After hes killed by the righteous leader of his own guild, Woojin gets a chance to start over. This time hes not interested in saving the world from monstershes got his sights set on revenge! His high-level kills quickly garner him notoriety among the game plebs, while boosting his stats as he masterminds his way closer to the top. But there's something no one can figure out: whose side hes playing for. Now that he knows how to play to win, Woojin will stop at nothing to destroy the hero!
(Source: Tapas)

As a powerful 8th class mage, Ian Paige took countless innocent lives under the orders of Emperor Ragnar, a close friend and ruler of the Greenriver Empire. Yet despite their closeness, Ragnar views Ian as a threat and subsequently poisons him. Using time magic, Ian saves himself and returns 30 years to the past. Now a young boy, Ian joins an elite order of mages to hone his abilities once again. This time, hell get revenge on the emperor who betrayed him and reclaim glory as an 8th class mage!
(Source: Tapas)
